oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Johnny Cash - Live in The Annex NCO Club - Tape 3
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Tape 3 of 3. Recording from tape features Johnny Cash (performer), Carl Perkins (performer) and June Carter (performer) performing on the Johnny Cash Show on an unknown date. Segment was recorded at the Annex 14 NCO Club in Long Binh, Vietnam.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Johnny Cash; June Cash; Carl Perkins
